sources.description:
It took six murdering rustlers and a girl to make a reckless rover settle down to love!
Dare Rudd and Dinkey Hooley, drifting cowhands, initially decline job offers from Dare's cousin Tom Fillmore in Montana. However, Dare changes his mind when he meets Tom's sweetheart, Judy Worstall, and ends up taking charge of a cattle drive, uncovering corruption along the way.
Can Dare Rudd prove he is responsible enough to win the heart of Judy and also outwit the crooked saloon owner?

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/tFyBqMk1zfE
